      "ANALOG FPV CAMERAS": "CRITICAL COMPATIBILITY NOTES:"
    },
    {
      "ANALOG FPV CAMERAS": "Key Point",
      "__EMPTY": "Description"
    },
    {
      "ANALOG FPV CAMERAS": "1. Analog Camera to VTX Compatibility",
      "__EMPTY": "ALL analog cameras are compatible with ALL analog VTX modules. They all use the standard composite video signal (NTSC or PAL). No frequency matching needed between camera and VTX."
    },
    {
      "ANALOG FPV CAMERAS": "2. Analog Camera to Goggle Compatibility",
      "__EMPTY": "Any analog camera + VTX combo works with ANY analog 5.8GHz goggle. The frequency band (A, B, E, F, C/Raceband) must be matched between VTX and Goggle receiver."
    },
    {
      "ANALOG FPV CAMERAS": "3. Frequency Bands Explained",
      "__EMPTY": "5.8GHz FPV uses multiple bands: Band A (CH1-8), Band B (CH1-8), Band E (CH1-8), Band F (CH1-8), Raceband (CH1-8). Most goggles support all bands with 40+ channels."
    },
    {
      "ANALOG FPV CAMERAS": "4. VTX Power Considerations",
      "__EMPTY": "Power output ranges from 25mW (limited range) to 1000mW (maximum range). Choose based on flying environment. Higher power = more heat and power consumption."
    },
    {
      "ANALOG FPV CAMERAS": "5. Receiver Module Upgrade",
      "__EMPTY": "Goggles with modular bays can use aftermarket receiver modules (RapidFire, Fusion, RapidMix) for better performance than stock receivers."
    },
    {
      "ANALOG FPV CAMERAS": "6. Display Technology Trade-offs",
      "__EMPTY": "OLED: Better contrast, faster response, better in low light. LCD: Lower cost, good brightness. LCOS: Middle ground option."
    },
    {
      "ANALOG FPV CAMERAS": "7. Input Voltage Critical",
      "__EMPTY": "Cameras need correct input voltage (check battery voltage). Low voltage = poor image quality. Use voltage regulators if needed."
    },
    {
      "ANALOG FPV CAMERAS": "8. 100% Compatible Setup Example",
      "__EMPTY": "Caddx Ant camera + Eachine TX805 VTX + FatShark Echo goggles = FULL COMPATIBILITY (all operate on 5.8GHz analog standard)"
    },
    {
      "ANALOG FPV CAMERAS": "9. Digital Systems NOT Compatible",
      "__EMPTY": "DJI, Walksnail, and HDZero are DIGITAL systems. Analog cameras/VTX cannot be used with digital goggles (and vice versa)."
    },
